paragraphs.text:
%sh
# download zip file to local file system, unzip it, and copy it to HDFS
sudo mkdir /data/tmp/strava
sudo chown zeppelin /data/tmp/strava
cd /data/tmp/strava
rm *.gpx
rm activities.zip
echo "donwloading activities.zip"
hadoop fs -get swift://journeyC.default/strava/raw/zip/DBAYARD.zip activities.zip
echo "unzipping"
unzip -q activities.zip
ls -l | head
echo "uploading individual activity files"
hadoop fs -mkdir -p strava/raw/DBAYARD
hadoop fs -put *.gpx strava/raw/DBAYARD/
hadoop fs -ls strava/raw/DBAYARD/ | head 
echo "done"

%pyspark
#https://github.com/larsbkrogvig/strava-spark/blob/master/py/preprocessing.ipynb
from pyspark.sql import Window, DataFrame
from pyspark.sql.functions import coalesce, concat, lag, lit, lower, sum, unix_timestamp, max, min, \
                                  sin, cos, atan, sqrt, atan2, toRadians, round, avg, first, expr, row_number, when
#read df from scala
df = DataFrame(z.get("myScalaDataFrame"), sqlContext)

# Timestamp in seconds
df = df.withColumn( 
    'TIME_unix_time', 
    unix_timestamp(df['time'], "yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ss'Z'")
)

# Partitioning on <athlete> and <activity_name>
window = Window.partitionBy('athlete', 'activityName', 'activityType').orderBy('TIME_unix_time')

def calculate_speed(df, window):
    
    # Time difference in seconds between tracking point and previous tracking point
    df = df.withColumn(
        'TIME_unix_time_diff',
        df['TIME_unix_time'] - lag('TIME_unix_time', count=1).over(window)
    )

    # Latitude and longditude in radians
    df = df.withColumn(
        'DIST_latR',
        toRadians(df['lat'])
    )
    df = df.withColumn(
        'DIST_lonR',
        toRadians(df['lon'])
    )
    
    # Latitude and longditude in previous tracking point
    df = df.withColumn(
        'DIST_latR_prev',
        lag('DIST_latR', count=1).over(window)
    )
    df = df.withColumn(
        'DIST_lonR_prev',
        lag('DIST_lonR', count=1).over(window)
    )
    
    # Difference in latitude and longditude since previous tracking point
    df = df.withColumn(
        'DIST_latR_diff',
        coalesce(df['DIST_latR'] - df['DIST_latR_prev'], lit(0))
    )
    df = df.withColumn(
        'DIST_lonR_diff',
        coalesce(df['DIST_lonR'] - df['DIST_lonR_prev'], lit(0))
    )

    # Havesine distance calculation between two tracking points
    df = df.withColumn(
        'DIST_a',
        sin(df['DIST_latR_diff']/2) * sin(df['DIST_latR_diff']/2)
        + cos(df['DIST_latR']) * cos(df['DIST_latR_prev'])
        * sin(df['DIST_lonR_diff']/2) * sin(df['DIST_lonR_diff']/2)
    )
    df = df.withColumn(
        'DIST_c',
        2 * atan2(sqrt(df['DIST_a']), sqrt(1 - df['DIST_a']))
    )
    
    R = 6371000 # Earth radius = 6371000 meters.  http://whatis.techtarget.com/definition/Earths-mean-radius
    
    # Distance between consecutive points
    df = df.withColumn(
        'DIST_diff_meters',
        coalesce(R * df['DIST_c'], lit(0))
    )
    
    # Momentary speed in km/h
    # 3.6 is 60minutes*60seconds divided by 1000m per KM
    df = df.withColumn(
        'SPEED_kmh',
        coalesce(
            3.6 * df['DIST_diff_meters'] / df['TIME_unix_time_diff'],
            lit(0)
        )
    )
    
    df = df.withColumn("SPEED_mph",
      expr("SPEED_kmh * 0.621371"))

    
    return df

%pyspark
df = calculate_speed(df, window)

pause_threshold_minutes = 0.5
rest_speed_threshold_kmh = {
    'Ride': 3,
    'Run': 2
}

for atype in rest_speed_threshold_kmh:
    df = df.filter( ~((df['activityType']==atype) & (df['SPEED_kmh']<rest_speed_threshold_kmh[atype])))

# Time difference in seconds between tracking point and previous tracking point
df = df.withColumn(
    'TIME_unix_time_diff',
    df['TIME_unix_time'] - lag('TIME_unix_time', count=1).over(window)
)

%pyspark
# Indicator (0,1) of whether time difference is greater than threshold (new activity block)
df = df.withColumn(
    'BLOCK_isnew',
    coalesce(
        (df['TIME_unix_time_diff'] >= pause_threshold_minutes * 60).cast('integer'),
        lit(0)
    )
)

# Sequence number of activity block per athlete and activity 
df = df.withColumn(
    'BLOCK_seqnum', 
    sum('BLOCK_isnew').over(window)
)

# Activity block id "<athlete>_<activityName>_<integer>"
df = df.withColumn(
    'BLOCK_id',
    concat(
        df['athlete'],
        lit('_'),
        lower(df['activityName']),
        lit('_'),
        df['BLOCK_seqnum'].cast('string')
    )
)

%pyspark
window_block = Window.partitionBy('BLOCK_id').orderBy('TIME_unix_time')

# Recalculate speed within each block
df = calculate_speed(df, window_block)

# Current total distance in km within the block
df = df.withColumn(
    'DIST_BLOCK_km',
    sum('DIST_diff_meters').over(window_block) / 1000
)

# Current total distance in km within the block
df = df.withColumn(
    'DIST_BLOCK_miles',
    sum('DIST_diff_meters').over(window_block) / 1000 * 0.621371
)

# Current time elapsed in seconds within the block
df = df.withColumn(
    'TIME_BLOCK_elapsed_seconds',
    df['TIME_unix_time'] - first(df['TIME_unix_time']).over(window_block)
)

# Compute rownum within block
df = df.withColumn(
    'BLOCK_rownum',
    row_number().over(window_block)    
)

# Compute a scale factor
df = df.withColumn(
    'scaleFactor',
    when(expr('BLOCK_rownum % 2048 = 0'),12).when(expr('BLOCK_rownum % 1024 = 0'),11).when(expr('BLOCK_rownum % 512 = 0'),10).when(expr('BLOCK_rownum % 256 = 0'),9).when(expr('BLOCK_rownum % 128 = 0'),8).when(expr('BLOCK_rownum % 64 = 0'),7).when(expr('BLOCK_rownum % 32 = 0'),6).when(expr('BLOCK_rownum % 16 = 0'),5).when(expr('BLOCK_rownum % 8 = 0'),4).when(expr('BLOCK_rownum % 4 = 0'),3).when(expr('BLOCK_rownum % 2 = 0'),2).otherwise(1)
)

%pyspark
dff = df.select(
    df['athlete'].alias('athlete'), 
    df['activityName'].alias('activityName'), 
    df['activityType'].alias('activityType'),
    df['BLOCK_id'].alias('block_id'),
    df['BLOCK_rownum'].alias('block_rownum'),
    df['scaleFactor'].alias('scaleFactor'),
    df['time'].alias('p_timestamp'),
    df['lat'].alias('p_latitude'), 
    df['lon'].alias('p_longditude'), 
    df['ele'].alias('p_elevation'),
    df['SPEED_kmh'].alias('p_speed_kmh'),
    df['SPEED_mph'].alias('p_speed_mph'),
    df['heart_rate'].alias('p_heart_rate'), 
    df['DIST_diff_meters'].alias('p_diff_distance_meters'),
    df['TIME_unix_time_diff'].alias('p_diff_time_seconds'),
    df['DIST_BLOCK_km'].alias('c_cumlative_distance_km'),
    df['DIST_BLOCK_miles'].alias('c_cumlative_distance_miles'),
    df['TIME_BLOCK_elapsed_seconds'].alias('c_elapsed_seconds')
)



dff.createOrReplaceTempView("temp_results")

dff.first()
